      "message": "As stated in the SDNC-1667: The problem is to use the subdirectory as volume. After doing thes the write rights for ODL-user are not there anymore. \nPlease modify the docker-compose to assign the two files like in the exmample below and it should work.\n volumes:\n - ./certs/certs.properties:/opt/opendaylight/certs/certs.properties\n - ./certs/keys0.zip:/opt/opendaylight/certs/keys0.zip",
